Subject: [PATCH] powerpc/code-patching: Fix KASAN hit by not flagging text
 patching area as VM_ALLOC

References: bsc#1215199 CVE-2025-21866 bsc#1239473
Patch-mainline: v6.14 or v6.14-rc4 (next release)
Git-commit: d262a192d38e527faa5984629aabda2e0d1c4f54

